## 🛠️ Task 01: Personal Portfolio Website

### 📋 Overview

This project is a **Personal Portfolio Website** designed to showcase my skills, projects, and achievements as a computer science student. The website features a modern and responsive design built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. It includes interactive elements and smooth navigation to provide a seamless user experience.

### 🚀 Live Preview

Explore the live version of the portfolio website here: [Personal Portfolio Website](https://waleedsid.netlify.app/)

### 🖼️ Screenshot

![Portfolio Website Screenshot](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/3f352091-9562-4f28-9506-48112817aace)

### 🔧 Features

- **Modern Design:** Clean and professional design with a focus on user experience.
- **Interactive Elements:** Smooth transitions and interactive components.
- **Project Showcase:** Highlights various projects and achievements.
- **Responsive Layout:** Optimized for both desktop and mobile devices.
- **Contact Form:** Allows visitors to get in touch via a built-in contact form.

### 🛠️ Technologies Used

- **HTML**: For the structure and content of the website.
- **CSS**: For styling and layout, ensuring a visually appealing design.
- **JavaScript**: For interactive elements and smooth transitions.

